review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2021
name: Susan Anderson
title: I can eat this without any digestive issues whatsoever.
review: I have issues with stomach cramping and can peal the paint off the wall, but I think you understand.I like everything about this cereal I can eat it cold for hot days or heat it up for cold days. It can be served with almost anything from fruit to spices, such as cinnamon.It is economical and a box lasts me a while. I am going to go ahead and sign up for auto ship as I cannot get it here.I received a box today and am glad because I ate the last of a box yesterday.It's good, just ask my happy tummy.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 10, 2021
name: The Rebecca Review
title: Crunchy Morning Cereal - Best with Cold Milk or Almond Milk
review: Weetabix is a cereal I remember from long ago and I used to make it with warm milk in the winter. In the spring and summer it is however delicious with cold milk and a little muscovado sugar sprinkled on top. It retains its crunchiness for quite a while and does not get mushy like with warm milk. I enjoy this in the morning with a mug of Jasmine tea.~The Rebecca Review

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2021
name: Amazon Customer
title: Good value
review: The 6 pack is a good value for money. The BBE is February 2021 which is less than the 180 days that Amazon holds 3rd party sellers accountable for. It's a BBE which is different from Expiry date so this will be good even after February 2021. If only buyers understands that a BBE is not an expiry date.
